...

444
00:21:25,595 --> 00:21:26,695
"Srećna sam."

445
00:21:28,129 --> 00:21:28,696
"Ja"

446
00:21:28,962 --> 00:21:29,462
"sam"

447
00:21:29,729 --> 00:21:30,262
"srećna".

448
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:34,129
Ovo neće biti lako.

449
00:21:35,363 --> 00:21:37,896
Univerzum ne reaguje na tvoje reči

450
00:21:38,763 --> 00:21:39,863
ali tvoje reči

451
